We are utilizing a specialized type for the foreground service because our use case does not fit within the predefined categories of foreground service types. We are registering a broadcast receiver within the battery animation service. Whenever the device connects to a charger, we initiate an activity where charging animations are displayed. This process cannot be paused; doing so would compromise the user experience. Users have downloaded the app specifically for uninterrupted battery animations.

This foreground service is dedicated to displaying a notification banner on the lock screen. It showcases wallpapers added to the app and is updated daily. To ensure users always have access to the latest wallpaper updates and notifications, this service operates continuously in the foreground. Interruptions or pauses in this service would disrupt the user experience and prevent timely updates of the lock screen content.

Welcome to the\n4K Wallpapers-Live Wallpapers App

Manage External Storage:
We require this permission to securely access the applied wallpaper so that you can view your wallpaper in launcher feature.

 System Alert Window:
This permission allows us to display a Battery Animation on homeScreen or on lockscreen whenever you plug your charger

 Query All Packages:
This permission is necessary for us to list all installed apps on your device. It enables us to offer functionalities such as opening another app from our launcher.

 Rest assured, your data is handled with the utmost care and is completely secure!
By continuing to use this app, you accept our privacy policy and terms of service.
If you disagree, you will be unable to use the app
